Toyota to Use Locally Made Hybrid Systems in China Production

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-22T04:57:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/toyota-to-use-locally-made-hybrid-systems-in-china-production.html
Toyota Motor Corp. (7203)  aims to develop
Chinese-made hybrid systems and start producing and selling cars
featuring the systems through its two joint ventures in  China 
around 2015, President  Akio Toyoda  said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
